    <h3>Description</h3>

    <div class="body">
        <p>In the documentation (documentation/manual/en/module_specs tree) chapter: 12.7.1. Controllers, something similar to the following can be added:</p>

<p>12.7.1.4 Custom Plugins Registration</p>

<p>The partial configuration below shows how to register custom plugins with the PluginLoader in the module configuration file:</p>

<pre class="highlight"><code>
return array(
   'di' =&gt; array(
        'instance' =&gt; array(
            'Zend\Mvc\Controller\PluginLoader' =&gt; array(
                'parameters' =&gt; array(
                    'map' =&gt; array(
                        'custom' =&gt; 'SomeCustomModule\CustomPlugin',
                ),
            ),
        ),
   ),
);
</code></pre>

